name: FajrAzan
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fajr azan
des:
This skill plays the Fajr Azan with a simple voice command. Simply say "Alexa, play Fajr Azan." or you can make a routine to play the Fajr Azan at a specific time or before sunrise. 

Don't forget to enable our skill for the other Azan!
https://www.amazon.com/Default-User-Al-Azan/dp/B08FC7XQNG
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
